  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Efficacy and Safety of Rituximab in Patients With Rheumatoid Arthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Multifactorial, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Dose-ranging Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Rituximab (MabThera速/Rituxan速) in Combination With Methotrexate in Patients With Active Rheumatoid Arthritis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
