  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess the efficacy and safety of different treatment regimens of rituximab
      (MabThera速/Rituxan速), corticosteroids, and placebo, combined with methotrexate (MTX), in
      patients with active rheumatoid arthritis (RA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
