  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Eligibility criteria include, but are not limited to the following:

          -  Are between the ages of 18 and 80 years.

          -  Have been diagnosed with rheumatoid arthritis for at least 6 months.

          -  Have failed treatment (lack of efficacy) with at least 1 but no more than 5
             disease-modifying anti-rheumatic drugs or biologics (other than methotrexate).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
